&lt;p&gt;It seems that changing the default behavior from &quot;no-follow&quot; to &quot;follow&quot; causes other problems (sanity test_56k in &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/49003&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/49003&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it OK to add &quot;&#8211;follow&quot; option to follow symlink and keep the original behavior (no-follow)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
